<h2>mastodon.sandwich.net</h2>
<p>This is <a href="https://www.sandwich.net/">Sandwich</a>'s public Mastodon instance. Welcome! Moderation is at our discretion - please see below.<br/>
<br/>
We recommend that you read <a href="https://mastodon.sandwich.net/tags/mastodonsandwich">the #MastodonSandwich hashtag</a> and <a href="https://sungo.io/users/sungo/updates/34">@sungo's toot about Mastodon's risks</a>. Feel free to chat with us about risk, privacy, security, and other questions.<br/>
<br/>
We support free and controversial speech, but also wish to maintain a pleasant environment. We forbid trolling, harassment, bigotry, and spam. Please use the Content Warning feature for NSFW or traumatic topics. When handling problems, we try to consider all of the circumstances, and to be reasonable and understanding.<br/>
<br/>
We will not sell your data, and will make every reasonable attempt to combat coerced disclosure of your data or our logs.</p>
